transforms.name: VisitType
transforms.expr: CASE WHEN ([ToBranchID] IN (508, 600, 305, 306, 307, 308, 309, 618, 617, 593, 594, 595, 596, 597, 598, 599) AND [ToGovernorateID] IN (9, 18)) THEN 'To IL' WHEN ([FromBranchID] IN (508, 600, 305, 306, 307, 308, 309, 618, 617, 593, 594, 595, 596, 597, 598, 599)) THEN 'From IL' WHEN ([FromBranchID] IN (315, 385, 384)) THEN 'From Allenby' WHEN ([ToBranchID] IN (315, 385, 384)) THEN 'To Allenby' WHEN ([FromGovernorateID] = [ToGovernorateID]) THEN 'In-City' ELSE 'Between Cities' END

transforms.name: SourceRegion

transforms.name: DestRegion
